about.description:
This package enables the CONDA_GO_COMPILER environment variable.
This variable is used by conda-forge's patched GoLang compiler to
set conda-aware GOBIN and GOPATH default values. These default
values are ignored if GOBIN and GOPATH environment variables
are set independently by the user.

For more details, please see the go-feedstock recipe.
about.summary: The Go (nocgo) compiler activation scripts for conda-build.

name: go-nocgo_win-64
raw_recipe:
# This file created by conda-build 3.19.2
# ------------------------------------------------

package:
    name: go-nocgo_win-64
    version: 1.13.10
source:
    -   folder: go
        patches:
            - patches/0001-issue10607-is-only-valid-when-running-with-CGO.patch
            - patches/0002-Fix-cgo_fortran-test-setup-for-conda.patch
            - patches/0003-Add-CC-C-CPP-LD-FLAGS-to-script_test-extraEnvKeys.patch
            - patches/0004-Inherit-CGO_-environment-variables.patch
            - patches/0005-Add-conda-aware-default-values-for-GOPATH-and-GOBIN.patch
        sha256: eb9ccc8bf59ed068e7eff73e154e4f5ee7eec0a47a610fb864e3332a2fdc8b8c
        url: https://dl.google.com/go/go1.13.10.src.tar.gz
build:
    binary_relocation: false
    detect_binary_files_with_prefix: false
    force_ignore_keys:
        - c_compiler
        - cxx_compiler
        - fortran_compiler
    missing_dso_whitelist:
        - $SYSROOT\System32\winmm.dll
    noarch: false
    number: '2'
    script: compiler/build.bat
    string: h75a39e6_2
requirements:
    run:
        - go 1.13.10 h0e7f9d5_2
test:
    script: compiler/test.bat
about:
    description: 'This package enables the CONDA_GO_COMPILER environment variable.

        This variable is used by conda-forge''s patched GoLang compiler to

        set conda-aware GOBIN and GOPATH default values. These default

        values are ignored if GOBIN and GOPATH environment variables

        are set independently by the user.


        For more details, please see the go-feedstock recipe.

        '
    dev_url: https://github.com/conda-forge/go-feedstock
    home: http://golang.org
    license: BSD-3-Clause
    license_family: BSD
    license_file: go/LICENSE
    summary: The Go (nocgo) compiler activation scripts for conda-build.
extra:
    copy_test_source_files: true
    final: true
    recipe-maintainers:
        - nehaljwani
        - scopatz
        - sodre
        - stuarteberg
